"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"The Ukrainian president is attending a Nato meeting in Turkey. He plans to ask for more interceptor missiles to help his country.\",            \"english_title\": \"Ukrainian President at Nato Meeting\",            \"translated_version\": \"El presidente de Ucrania est\u00e1 en una reuni\u00f3n de la OTAN en Turqu\u00eda. Planea pedir m\u00e1s misiles para ayudar a su pa\u00eds.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Presidente de Ucrania en reuni\u00f3n de la OTAN\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Two former Syrian officials are on trial in Vienna, Austria. They are accused of crimes against people who opposed the former Syrian leader Bashar al-Assad.\",            \"english_title\": \"Syrian Officials on Trial\",            \"translated_version\": \"Dos exfuncionarios sirios est\u00e1n en juicio en Viena, Austria. Est\u00e1n acusados de cr\u00edmenes contra personas que se opusieron al exl\u00edder sirio Bashar al-Assad.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Exfuncionarios sirios en juicio\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Tour de France organizers have banned spectators from stage three. This decision was made because a wildfire is affecting the Pyr\u00e9n\u00e9es-Orientales region.\",            \"english_title\": \"Tour de France Bans Spectators\",            \"translated_version\": \"Los organizadores del Tour de Francia han prohibido espectadores en la etapa tres. Esta decisi\u00f3n se tom\u00f3 porque un incendio est\u00e1 afectando la regi\u00f3n de Pyr\u00e9n\u00e9es-Orientales.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Tour de Francia proh\u00edbe espectadores\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Interpol reports that most of the 2,070 victims or potential victims identified are women. They are being trafficked for sex.\",            \"english_title\": \"Interpol on Human Trafficking\",            \"translated_version\": \"Interpol informa que la mayor\u00eda de las 2,070 v\u00edctimas o posibles v\u00edctimas identificadas son mujeres. Est\u00e1n siendo traficadas para sexo.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Interpol sobre tr\u00e1fico de personas\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Fabiana was trapped in the rubble of a 10-storey residential building. This happened after two earthquakes hit Venezuela in June.\",            \"english_title\": \"Fabiana Trapped After Earthquakes\",            \"translated_version\": \"Fabiana qued\u00f3 atrapada en los escombros de un edificio residencial de 10 pisos. Esto pas\u00f3 despu\u00e9s de dos terremotos en Venezuela en junio.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Fabiana atrapada tras terremotos\"        }    ]}"